![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6fd110b3-9dd8-4875-9471-131a9bc54ab3/22392.jpg)

CM Punk opens WWE RAW as World Champion for the first time since January of 2013

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8b134eb0-eae6-4839-8948-3eb64f6fb6fb/22396.jpg)

Huge YOU DESERVE IT chants for the new World Heavyweight Champion.

CM Punk thanks the fans. His wife. And Main Event Jey Uso. Punk hopes they can be friends moving forward but he understands if they can't be.. as Punk said in the past, he was not in WWE to make friends.

Summerslam taught CM Punk to hold onto the World Heavyweight Championship tightly. But there's no Seth Rollins to ruin it this time.

Punk mocks Rollins by doing his championship belt swing above his head. Punk says when Rollins returns, if he gets in Punk's business. Punk will put him back on the DL

Punk understands there's a target on his back. He wants to be a fighting champion. Punk wants to test himself against the best.

The Champ. Is. Here.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8be6fad7-a168-47ac-9bf8-f0e828505de6/22404.jpg)

CM Punk said he wanted to defend against anyone... He got Logan Paul.

Punk says NOOOO... No no no.. He says Paul should take up Ilja Dragunov on his US Open Challenge. That's more his speed. Paul says he's taken on John Cena and Roman Reigns, he's beaten AJ Styles . He deserves a shot.

Paul Heyman interrupted with the Vision.. Heyman doesn't see a king in the ring, he sees a bitch without an owner and he's talking about Logan Paul.

Paul is not the future. He's not the front of the line. Bron Breakker and Bronson Reed are at the front of the line. Heyman reminds Punk when THEY were the World Champion, Heyman was not the one who lost THEIR title.

Logan Paul is in the wrong place at the wrong time. He needs to move or get hurt. Logan says he was out first he's not going anywhere.

Bron Breakker grabs the mic, thanks CM Punk for keeping them off TV for two weeks until a new champ was crowned. Bron wants the World Championship.

The only things in the way are a YouTuber and an old man. Punk asks Paul to fight at his side, Paul declines and tries to run away but Bron Breakker shoves him to the ground.

Paul decides to help CM Punk! But he gets a Tsunami for his efforts before Punk finally gets back in the ring to help clear it.

