## Rey Mysterio has returned from injury to confront his son Dominik!!!!!

## **_REY: How can you be the greatest Luchador of all time? What about El Santo? Blue Demon? Eddie Guerrero?_**

## **_DOM: "You keep my father's name OUT OF YOUR MOUTH!"_**

Rey Mysterio says he can respect Dominik but he has to draw the line when Dom calls himself the King of the Luchadors.

Dom insults their family name when he says this.

Dom says yes, he's better than El Santo, Blue Demon and Eddie Guerrero. And he's DEFINITELY better than Rey Mysterio.

Rey says he's going to leave... But as long as Rey is around, Dom will NEVER be king of the Luchadors, this will NEVER be Dom's ring, and Dom will NEVER be the greatest Mysterio.

The brawl begins and doesn't stop until Rey hits the 619 and Dom rolls out of the ring to safety.

> Rey: \*mentions Eddie Guerrero"  
>   
> Dom: "KEEP MY FATHERS NAME OUT OF YOUR MOUTH!"  
