*   ## **_WWE World Tag Team Championships: AJ Styles and Dragon Lee def. Judgement Day_**
    

Dominik Mysterio came out mid match to give th Judgement Day the advantage but he wasn't very helpful.

And that was before Sheamus ran out to get rid of Dominik to even the odds so AJ Styles could hit the Styles Clash on JD McDonough for the win

